{"tid":1505764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家一齊跳閘","createTime":"2019-08-25T15:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:33:47.000Z","uid":263900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e5745d121fccd7dd03fb015146029f1023c91c","tid":1505764,"uid":263900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"返工時間只要多人做就會大家跟住做 <br />\n香港人最驚蝕抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a006ab76654bcb6b2ff08dd61e02ac6c690d27a7","tid":1505764,"uid":263900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"P牌push"},{"pid":"41039e8c97bf5d458a7d28fdf6cad0ab75b22954","tid":1505764,"uid":147536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"小弟聽日返工帶返個口罩先跳 希望見到同路人"},{"pid":"b14c39f29c759e9156512f454cb7033447ea5b51","tid":1505764,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"跳閘哨兵 TG group"},{"pid":"e69595ccacc807fea34bd54588490ef8582537a9","tid":1505764,"uid":257447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:15:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">P牌狗借位，大家覺得有用請幫手開新Post呼籲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會考慮吓呼籲全世界平日返工放工都跳閘</span><br />\n<br />\n其實「黨鐵」咁樣封半條線，仲要擺明比狗爛運兵車用<br />\n<br />\n會唔會考慮吓呼籲全世界平日返工放工都跳閘<br />\n一兩個人做就會比人搞<br />\n個個都做嘅話點睇？<br />\n文宣會唔會考慮下？<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點先做得起，先講個諗法出嚟<br />\n睇下有冇人做到，呼籲下<br />\n自己人微言輕，唔知點煲大佢<br />\n長者八達通個效果唔明顯<br />\n但跳閘就唔同講法<br />\n又唔洗搵前線打開個閘位，減低前線承受嘅風險，只要肯跳夠多人就做到<br />\n唔單單係星期六日抗爭先做<br />\n係要平日返工放工嘅時候都做<br />\n<br />\n我有呢一個諗法，但唔知點樣煲大佢<br />\n所以先講出嚟睇吓大家有冇D乜嘢諗法</span>"},{"pid":"da56224b4bac3b8483c820219ede3629779db574","tid":1505764,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武後勤全面升級！</span><br />\n<br />\n早排返鄉下打獵，見到成班小朋友淨係掉雜物/用碌竹去打<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506054\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8577c45a60eaf8a66c9d3b0df568f542fb00b293","tid":1505764,"uid":251811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">防暴</span><span style=\"color: red;\">衝入不反對通知書集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［有片］和理非俾人恰到上喉嚨掟啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506031</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}